 Volvo (publ)\">OTCPK:VLVLY</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VOLAF\" title=\"AB Volvo (publ)\">OTCPK:VOLAF</a>), a Swedish manufacturer of trucks, buses, construction vehicles, renowned for quality via safety, has been somewhat away from the spotlight of the industry. The company is suffering from stagnation in the European market and a decline</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1271521953/image_1271521953.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747551-volvo-may-take-a-hit-in-2025-but-investors-can-still-come-out-ahead", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 01:52:59", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747549", "title": "Larimar Therapeutics: Positive Friedreich's Ataxia Data Can Only Get Better", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rear view and close up image of Young Scientist researcher stirs the substance in the beaker while discussing the result with a colleague\" data-id=\"2177260462\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/217726046