om/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183067044/image_2183067044.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183067044/image_2183067044.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183067044/image_2183067044.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183067044/image_2183067044.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183067044/image_2183067044.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183067044/image_2183067044.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183067044/image_2183067044.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183067044/image_2183067044.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kevin Frayer/Getty Images News</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>One company that I have been quite bullish about recently is <strong>Lithia Motors</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LAD\" title=\"Lithia Motors, Inc.\">LAD</a></span>). For those not familiar with the firm, it operates as one of the largest global automotive retailers out there. In addition</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183067044/image_2183067044.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747544-lithia-motors-solid-prospect-in-spite-of-certain-weaknesses", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 01:20:11", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747541", "title": "United Airlines: Why I Sold My Shares (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"United Airlines\" data-id=\"1199330088\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Rusell Hendry</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In early October I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725485-united-airlines-stock-hold-after-recent-take-off\">wrote my first article</a> about United Airlines (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UAL\" title=\"United Airlines Holdings, Inc.\">UAL</a></span>) highlighting why I thought that the recent price appreciation (between August and October) deemed the stock a Hold. Since I was personally invested at the time, I mentioned</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1199330088/image_1199330088.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747541-united-airlines-ual-why-i-sold-my-shares-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 01:13:56", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747540", "title": "BHP Group: Solid Free Cash Flow Supports The Yield, Shares Rightly Priced", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Steelworker cleaning pouring end of flask during steel pour in steelworks\" data-id=\"1186090888\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Monty Rakusen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span>Iron ore prices were down sharply in 2024; it was the worst year for the industrial commodity </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4391753-iron-ore-caps-worst-annual-drop-since-2015-on-weak-china-demand-high-portside-stocks\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span>since 2015</span></a><span>. A strong US dollar and broad economic weakness in key developed, and emerging countries couldn\u2019t support the price. Not surprisingly, shares</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1186090888/image_1186090888.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747540-bhp-group-solid-free-cash-flow-supports-the-yield", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 01:08:05", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747539", "title": "Avery Dennison: Labeling A Better Future", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Avery Dennison manufacturing plant. Avery Dennison is the largest label manufacturer in the world II\" data-id=\"1162604424\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1162604424/image_1162604424.jpg